Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to the Maiden Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where he was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has been left with Dadan - \Nthe mountain bandit of Mt. Corvo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and met 2 precocious kids named Ace and Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leaving the Dadan Family for Good?! \NThe Kids' Hideout Has Been Built!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you, Pochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who dug a hole at the front door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Ace and the other \Ntwo - to catch boars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my house! They can't just \Ndig a hole wherever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, who gave you permission \Nto invade our territory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your territory?! Ha! You \Nguys are so full of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense and bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the sheriff! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, Hurry up! It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a deer for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I love venison! Let's go hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come home, annoying brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mealtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out until you count up to 10,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do a major \Nhousecleaning every night after dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick them out at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Wait, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only time I can relax \Nis when I'm in my futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last training for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy, are you alive?\N--What a crappy floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta kick the brats out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, they're gonna \Ntake over the Dadan family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, it's ruining my health!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got control over us long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's just I can't \Nlook after them anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm gonna kick them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the agreement with Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry! I don't \Nknow what made me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. I heard that Luffy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 6 months so we came \Nhere to see how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Garp-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really living with the bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a big one! You're a bandit \N- don't give me attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! People from the \NWindmill Village are all annoying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some presents for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that Garp-san wouldn't \Nthink about these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is! New clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll adjust the length \Nso... I need you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Ace-kun was mischievous
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you seem like a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's so shy!\N--You're blushing, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You jerks!\N--Oh hey, you can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meals should be good on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get the best cook first \Nthing when I go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a pirate before \Nyou do so just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair! I'm gonna \Nbecome a pirate first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying a crap like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you both understand that \Nyou must become Navy soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dadan!\N--Yes, Garp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I get hit, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not educating the brats well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Garp? He's Ace and Luffy's grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squirt, you mentioned about \Ngoing out to sea, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a "Squirt" - he's Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We exchanged a cup of sake and \Npledged to become pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has such a big mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that means now there are 3 fools
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who want me to give them a real workout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy, Luffy. \NYou have 2 older brothers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This old man is like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for today! I'm \Ngonna be harsher tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't drop dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, the old \Nman will kill us tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll keep doing it until \Nwe give up our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to make up our minds, brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We will stand on our feet."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How smart-alecky of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you not care?! They're \Ninfamous even downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone will try to kill them on sight \Nif they aren't sheltered by us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My vacation is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta shape them into full-fledged \NNavy men by the time I come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you gonna leave everything to me again?!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a bandit raise a Navy soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer doesn't know what he's saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are worrying about \Nthose kids after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Come to think \Nof it, this is good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left voluntarily! Oh, I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got away successfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming - Dadan and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that  "the devil's \Nchildren have the devil's luck"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the devil's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that she feels happy now \Nbecause her troubles have gone away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It's pouring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay here and hide from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind. I don't \Nwanna get beaten by Garp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and look for the stupid brats already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I designed our hideout. We can't \Nsleep outdoors forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we gotta build a hideout right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hideout... That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got tons you-know-where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Looks exactly like the design!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great work if I say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hideout so we \Ngotta set up some traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a view of the Gray Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Windmill Village and \Nthe water of the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so uncommon, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to see them from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's different!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, there's a tailwind! Set the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance to the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy off the bow and starboard side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bluejam's ship! Prepare for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've started shooting! \NTake evasive action!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, hard aport!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You have to say "steady" \Nat times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, hard aport!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard aport! Steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight hand-to-hand! Lay aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for them to come aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can't you find them yet?!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked to people who saw them at \Nthe Gray Terminal or in the jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 2 weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they were eaten by the \Nbig tiger in the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--W-We found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They built a hideout in the \Nhuge tree deep in the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm happy for you, boss!\N--You were worrying so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! Are they still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that those \Nbrats are so tenacious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand around, guys! \NGo get something for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Sabo... Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're sleeping, they \Nlook like ordinary kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, don't catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap just went off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone tried to invade already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Maybe it was just a glitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we made it in hurry so it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never worry about them again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the boys are attacked by a huge \Nbear, a certain old man saves them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man tells them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he once fought Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is thrilled to hear a story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the Pirate King that \Nhe's never heard before!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Becoming an Apprentice?! A Man Who \NFought Against the King of the Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
