Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Freedom Taken Away! The Nobles' \NPlot Closing in on the Brothers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready for it! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool! It's getting windier and windier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, hold on to the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's uncool for pirates to \Nhave their flag blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Come on, wild wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, violent storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! We survived the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the hideout's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go and collect materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find that kind \Nof thing there, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather find a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be cool if we could find one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Ace. I can't find a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, we're not here for a telescope. \NLook for building materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a telescope! Luffy's gonna be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that one of \Nthe three infamous brats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys. But don't leave a mark on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I feel dizzy...\N--You okay, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the three of us fight together, \Nwe can easily beat these fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We even beat \Nthe big tiger of Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just finish this up \Nby killing their captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, brats, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn! Let me go!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away! Or I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I barely made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't harm a hair on him, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn! You...!\N--Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to find me so \Nbadly that he hired pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they are the ones who \Ntempted Sabo into evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "give him \Nback"? Sabo is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids have to live as their parents say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the parents brought \Nthem into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you two tempt Sabo to run away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thug-wannabe brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you after my money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirate! Be careful about hitting a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got that trashy kid's blood all over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Nobody tempted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away of my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this! Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest up to you, pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, mister. You've \Nalready paid us for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of these two so \Nthey won't bother your boy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Bluejam! \NDad, that's enough! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as you say. I'll \Nlive as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very important to \Nme,  they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop playing pirate. \NIt's just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, run! You don't have to worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanna live freely with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! What should we do with these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take them to our hideout.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me again! I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice to be a noble, \Ndon't you think so, brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look down on others as if they're \Ntrash and boss everyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a pirate is way better! \NThat's what Sabo said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling bad for you \Nguys. Hey, untie them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think a kid from a noble family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,escaped to a place like Gray Terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it as a mockery of the people \Nhere just like noble adults do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he was looking down on you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Sabo wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! We're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Alright, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not gonna bother \Nthat brat, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're planning on doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd \Nhave to kill both of you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of him as your brother, \Nit's best to leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sabo's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sabo hates the High Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to let go of him if \Nyou really care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when you get older. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an axe to grind with you \Nabout what you did to Porchemy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can forget about it. I rather \Nliked your show of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to ask you something. \NI think you might be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm short-handed now. \NDo you guys wanna work for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's an easy task. \NIt's not dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a map of Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just have to carry packages \Nto the locations marked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much will you pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, I don't like it when Sabo is not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live with it. I don't like it, \Neither. I wanna rescue Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what is really best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how things go. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't take it there, \Nhe can just come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make some money for the \Npirate savings for that occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it. It's not \NAce and Luffy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you tell the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because they warned \Nyou not to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not those kinds of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a criminal record, it \Ndamages your family's reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't enter High Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tempted by those two,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having no choice but to \Nget involved in violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,weren't you, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of your friends in the Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in the hands of those pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can give them an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're that important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,think about what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart boy. \NYou know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised that you wouldn't hurt them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime is a crime! We did \Nit of our own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad to have such a stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand my dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sabo, let's go. It's been \Na long while since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't go in yet - you're filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wash and disinfect your \Nbody in the yard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're safe, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sabo! You're back. You got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Stelly, say "hi" to your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, brother! \NMy name is Stelly and I'm 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We adopted him. He's a smart \Nboy from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, his \Nparents became negligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we took him in since \Nhe's full of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't work out to be my successor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm telling you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to start studying tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brother! I heard that \Nyou're pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother and father were always \Nsaying that behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have the devil's luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'cuz they're gonna take care of \Nthe burnables tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had stayed in the Gray Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would've died tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it would've been better for me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if their real son didn't come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you doing?! I'll tell father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's gonna be a fire in \Nthe Gray Terminal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A fire?!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know about \Nit because you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they decided it months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has sent a group of observers \Nto go around the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna arrive in Goa \NKingdom finally 3 days from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they have a World Noble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Celestial Dragon with them \Nso people are panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the royal family \Ndon't want him to see our stigma,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they decided to burn \Ndown the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this country will be clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking \Nabout? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people living there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't take away their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna burn up all \Nthe shame of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, the people, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just jump down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It is not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! He must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible to burn \Ndown an area so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were from this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we ready for tomorrow? \NThere can't be any miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready but the unknown \Nfactor is the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to burn the trash precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam's clan is setting \Nboxes of oil and explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all over the Gray Terminal up \Nuntil the appointed time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam has a hand in this? \NThen it must be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how's Sabo doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed to let go of Sabo for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be better for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can figure out if there'll be a fire or not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the look of people in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hi, good morning!\N--Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Isn't it a lovely morning.\N--Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh great! There is nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk around the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning should be \Nmore lovely, shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems normal as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is windy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accidents could easily happen on a \Nday like this - especially fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo is not in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still wants to keep playing \Npirate without studying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't have gotten out \Nof the town so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me, mister.\N--What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that there'll be a \Nfire in the Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which family are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here? \NEverybody knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all know about it and \Nthey're acting normally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone care about the \Nfire in the Gray Terminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to carry the boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and there will be a \Nbig task for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad knows about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he brought me \Nback - before the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he wants me to maintain their status
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and inherit their property even \Nthough he thinks I'm a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry if my dog is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of breath. What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you know that there'll be a \Nfire in the Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone in this town \Nincluding you look concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does no one try to prevent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you're a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have to keep quiet about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone outside the \Ntown finds out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're special! If you're \Nfrom a noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong \Nwith this town! Everybody's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they know that \Npeople will die soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they act normally and even smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna stay here! \NI gotta tell them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today of all days, it's windy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Isn't it him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt! That's the runaway boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in this country \Nare planning to burn up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their national shame tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get out of the \NGray Terminal! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning the secret \Nbehind the fire outbreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are pushed into \Ndire straits by Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo rushes into Gray Terminal to save them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the intensely burning flames
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are about to devour Luffy and Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fire Has Been Set! \NThe Gray Terminal in Crisis!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
